# 一、大数定律与中心极限定理
{: id="20260305082132-bkr8msa" updated="20260305082132"}

## （一）大数定律
{: id="20260305082132-8oehnfh" updated="20260305082132"}

对随机变量序列 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{X_{n}\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，记
{: id="20260305082132-yhx9psg" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\overline{X_{n}}=\dfrac{1}{n}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_{i}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-w3hdg3e" updated="20260305082132"}

若存在常数序列 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{a_{n}\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，对任意的 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\varepsilon&amp;gt;0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，有
{: id="20260305082132-u0qwabp" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\{|\overline{X_{n}}-a_n|<\varepsilon\}=1
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-0jgleu3"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X_n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 服从大数定律。
{: id="20260305082132-kciycrz" updated="20260305082132"}

> 一般的，常数序列取为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="a_n=E\overline{X_n}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
> {: id="20260305082132-841lwwv" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-67uxoa4" updated="20260305082132"}

### 1.切比雪夫大数定律
{: id="20260305082132-rcf290i" updated="20260305082132"}

设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{X_n\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是互不相关的随机变量，具有相同的期望和方差
{: id="20260305082132-8wky7v3" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge EX_i=\mu, DX_i=\sigma^2
$$
{: id="20260305082132-bf3qq47" updated="20260305082132"}

则随机变量服从大数定律，即
{: id="20260305082132-peqljie" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\{|\overline{X_n}-\mu|<\varepsilon\}=1
$$
{: id="20260305082132-pybtax3" updated="20260305082132"}

### 2.辛钦大数定律
{: id="20260305082132-luu7bko" updated="20260305082132"}

设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{X_n\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是独立同分布的随机变量序列，若期望 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="EX_n=\mu" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 有限，则对任意 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\varepsilon&amp;gt;0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，有
{: id="20260305082132-jik6v1e" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\{|\dfrac{1}{n}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i-\mu|<\varepsilon\}=1
$$
{: id="20260305082132-b7s7xn2" updated="20260305082132"}

### 3.伯努利大数定律
{: id="20260305082132-q3d2f7i" updated="20260305082132"}

设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n_A" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 次独立重复试验中事件 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="A" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 发生的次数，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="p" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是每次试验中事件 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="A" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 发生的概率，则对任意 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\varepsilon&amp;gt;0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，有
{: id="20260305082132-kz1eeir" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\{|\dfrac{n_A}{n}-p|<\varepsilon\}=1
$$
{: id="20260305082132-5exsvy7" updated="20260305082132"}

## （二）中心极限定律
{: id="20260305082132-60g5ph0" updated="20260305082132"}

### 1.独立同分布的中心极限定理（Lévy-Lindeberg 中心极限定理）
{: id="20260305082132-hq2slws" updated="20260305082132"}

随机变量 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{X_n\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 相互独立同分布，且具有数学期望和方差
{: id="20260305082132-wlylq15" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge EX_i=\mu, DX_i=\sigma^2
$$
{: id="20260305082132-pv8pgvm" updated="20260305082132"}

则
{: id="20260305082132-qrqcj6c" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\left(\dfrac{\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i-n\mu}{\sigma\sqrt{n}}\leq x\right)=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^xe^{-t^2/2}\text{d}t
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ravrn2z" updated="20260305082132"}

> 当 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 充分大时，有
> {: id="20260305082132-o7gg6vi" updated="20260305082132"}
>
> $$
> \huge\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i\overset{近似}{\sim}N(n\mu,n\sigma^2)
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-arnpggm" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-m3xyxtu" updated="20260305082132"}

### 2.De Moivre-Laplace 中心极限定理
{: id="20260305082132-f2rljtw" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 重伯努利试验中，事件 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="A" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 每次出现的概率为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="p" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，出现的次数为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\eta_n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，则
{: id="20260305082132-zt8zj7l" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\left(\dfrac{\eta_n-np}{\sqrt{np(1-p)}}\leq x\right)=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^xe^{-t^2/2}\text{d}t
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ucm3mby" updated="20260305082132"}

> 当 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 充分大时，有
> {: id="20260305082132-nuwmz82" updated="20260305082132"}
>
> $$
> \huge\eta_n\overset{近似}{\sim}N(np,np(1-p))
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-kxxvkls" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-d9pljzw"}

### 3.Liapunov 中心极限定理
{: id="20260305082132-60xcsmv" updated="20260305082132"}

设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\{X_n\}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 相互独立，他们的期望方差存在
{: id="20260305082132-abni5e7" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge EX_i=\mu_i, DX_i=\sigma^2_i\neq0
$$
{: id="20260305082132-rqyu3n7" updated="20260305082132"}

记
{: id="20260305082132-c92xnvl" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge B^2_n=\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sigma^2_i
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-gblm4f6"}

若存在 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\delta&amp;gt;0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，使
{: id="20260305082132-toah8cr" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\dfrac{1}{B_n^{2+\delta}}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}E\left[\left|X_i-\mu_i\right|^{2+\delta}\right]=0
$$
{: id="20260305082132-2me3yil" updated="20260305082132"}

则有
{: id="20260305082132-bu14ezp" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P\left(\dfrac{\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i-\displaystyle\sum_{i-1}^n\mu_i}{B_n}\leq x\right)=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^xe^{-t^2/2}\text{d}t
$$
{: id="20260305082132-070vy9g" updated="20260305082132"}

> 在定理条件下，当 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 充分大时，有
> {: id="20260305082132-vvb0lpu" updated="20260305082132"}
>
> $$
> \huge\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i\overset{近似}{\sim}N(\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^n\mu_i,B^2_n)
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-36u7s2l" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-wzudrsb" updated="20260305082132"}

# 二、数理统计
{: id="20260305082132-aebus4g" updated="20260305082132"}

## （一）总体与样本
{: id="20260305082132-mtl932g" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">总体</span>：研究对象的全体组成的集合
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-z303uez"}

<span data-type="strong">个体</span>：组成总体的每个元素
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-0bfes6j"}

<span data-type="strong">样本</span>：<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的一个<span data-type="strong">容量</span>为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的样本
{: id="20260305082132-b2raj78" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">理论分布函数</span>：总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的分布函数
{: id="20260305082132-wmeuode" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">经验分布函数</span>：将样本观测值 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(x_1,x_2,\cdots,x_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 从小到大排列为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="x_1^*\leq x_2^*\leq\cdots\leq x_n^*" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
{: id="20260305082132-zsce658" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge F_n(x)=\begin{cases}
0 & x<x_1^* \\
\dfrac{k}{n} & x_k^*\leq x<x_{k+1}^*\quad(k=1,2,\cdots,n-1) \\
1 & x\geq x_n^*
\end{cases}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-p2gpwy8" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">统计量</span>：<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="g(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，其中 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="g" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为不含未知参数的连续函数
{: id="20260305082132-8ck4c2o" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-hzyhufz" updated="20260305082132"}样本均值
  {: id="20260305082132-lhlp2d9" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-cos40sv" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\overline{X}=\dfrac{1}{n}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i
$$
{: id="20260305082132-8eizmqr" updated="20260305082132"}

> $$
> \huge E(\overline{X})=\mu\quad D(\overline{X})=\dfrac{\sigma^2}{n}
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-qxbitv0" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-39fcvz3"}

- {: id="20260305082132-5ykt2cb" updated="20260305082132"}样本方差
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-ferhs49"}
{: id="20260305082132-76td4uh" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge S^2=\dfrac{1}{n-1}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}(X_i-\overline{X})^2
$$
{: id="20260305082132-48dkehg" updated="20260305082132"}

> $$
> \huge E(S^2)=\sigma^2\quad D(S^2)=\dfrac{\nu_4}{n}-\dfrac{(n-3)\sigma^4}{n(n-1)}
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-ls60iiv" updated="20260305082132"}
>
> $$
> \huge \nu_4=E[X-E(X)]^4
> $$
> {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-5qx2j7i"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-6zbbunt" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-nt5wf8e" updated="20260305082132"}样本 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 阶原点矩
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-s3g1o7l"}
{: id="20260305082132-b7bwe7m" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge A_n=\dfrac{1}{n}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i^k
$$
{: id="20260305082132-w3c2yp6" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-f84fb4p" updated="20260305082132"}样本 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 阶中心矩
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-si8481n"}
{: id="20260305082132-gt98rh3" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge B_n=\dfrac{1}{n}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{n}(X_i-\overline{X})^k
$$
{: id="20260305082132-e48aqao" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-pn4eo06" updated="20260305082132"}顺序统计量
  将样本的一组观测值从小到大排列为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="x_1^*\leq x_2^*\leq\cdots\leq x_n^*" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，令 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X_i^*=x_i^*" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，称为第 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="i" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 位统计量
  {: id="20260305082132-kbh4dg3" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-pulo5nl" updated="20260305082132"}样本中位数
  {: id="20260305082132-nr5gcti" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-5dlqw2n" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\widetilde{X}=\begin{cases}
X^*_{m+1} & n=2m+1 \\
\dfrac{1}{2}(X^*_{m}+X^*_{m+1}) & n=2m
\end{cases}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ypidmqt" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-o8f0zbs" updated="20260305082132"}样本极差
  {: id="20260305082132-e8n0j2j" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-8ei9aq4" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge R=X^*_{n}-X^*_{1}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-wr6l72o" updated="20260305082132"}

## （二）抽样分布
{: id="20260305082132-64de215" updated="20260305082132"}

### <span data-type="strong">1.</span><span data-type="strong inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\chi^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span><span data-type="strong"> 分布</span>
{: id="20260305082132-q6bumdx" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是来自正态总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="N(0,1)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的样本，则有
{: id="20260305082132-d12sxti" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\chi^2=\sum_{i=1}^nX_i^2\sim\chi^2(n)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ryjwxtm" updated="20260305082132"}

其概率密度为
{: id="20260305082132-r0rq8na" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge
f(x)=
\begin{cases}
\dfrac{1}{2^{n/2}\Gamma(n/2)}x^{\frac{n}{2}-1}e^{-\frac{x}{2}}, & x\geq0\\
0, & x<0
\end{cases}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-sqh7wox" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">性质</span>：
{: id="20260305082132-dopzkcy" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-eprch4w"}数字特征
  {: id="20260305082132-4yvj3ep" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-53sv6j5" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge E(\chi^2)=n\quad D(\chi^2)=2n
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ikxfkch" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-tk61i8v"}分布可加性
  设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\chi^2_1\sim\chi^2(n_1),\chi^2_2\sim\chi^2(n_2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 且相互独立，则有
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-ypa17g5"}
{: id="20260305082132-042gjjs" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\chi^2_1+\chi^2_2\sim\chi^2(n_1+n_2)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-xwlo8s0" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-r22b7gy"}近似计算
  当 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 充分大 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(n&amp;gt;45)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 时，有
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-1toeeyk"}
{: id="20260305082132-3f3e28a" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \sqrt{2\chi^2}\overset{近似}{\sim}N(\sqrt{2n-1},1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-vsp4wjx" updated="20260305082132"}

上 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\alpha" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 分位数
{: id="20260305082132-h7p28vh" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge\chi^2_{\bar{\alpha}}(n)\approx\dfrac{1}{2}(z_\bar\alpha+\sqrt{2n-1})^2
$$
{: id="20260305082132-3luknok" updated="20260305082132"}

### 2.<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="t" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 分布
{: id="20260305082132-jz31run" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X\sim N(0,1),Y\sim\chi^2(n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 且相互独立，则有
{: id="20260305082132-c3ee7p7" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge T=\dfrac{X}{\sqrt{Y/n}}\sim t(n)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-dgcfvpo" updated="20260305082132"}

其概率密度为
{: id="20260305082132-rbfbiu0" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge
f(x)=\dfrac{\Gamma((n+1)/2)}{\sqrt{n\pi}\Gamma(n/2)}\left(1+\dfrac{x^2}{n}\right)^{-(n+1)/2},\quad -\infty<x<+\infty
$$
{: id="20260305082132-nbeu8fe" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">性质</span>
{: id="20260305082132-ckufmzr" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-93zn2r0" updated="20260305082132"}图像性质
  {: id="20260305082132-pmhzy2f" updated="20260305082132"}
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-ccywy47"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="f(x)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为偶函数，且有
{: id="20260305082132-ff1nicq" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \lim_{|x|\rightarrow+\infty}f(x)=0\quad\lim_{n\rightarrow+\infty}f(x)=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}e^{-\frac{x^2}{2}}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-476m33j" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-n5th72a" updated="20260305082132"}近似计算
  当 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="n&amp;gt;45" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 时，有
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-0dw5gsy"}
{: id="20260305082132-fhckef2" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge t_\bar\alpha(n)\approx z_\bar\alpha
$$
{: id="20260305082132-fz00a9q" updated="20260305082132"}

### 3.<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="F" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 分布
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-ld6yxfu"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X\sim\chi^2(n_1),Y\sim\chi^2(n_2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 且相互独立，则有
{: id="20260305082132-gyddad2" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge F=\dfrac{X/n_1}{Y/n_2}\sim F(n_1,n_2)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-mpo2g9v" updated="20260305082132"}

其概率密度为
{: id="20260305082132-z52yjkx" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
f(x)=
\begin{cases}
\dfrac{\Gamma\left[\left(n_1+n_2\right)/2\right]}{\Gamma(n_1/2)\Gamma(n_2/2)}\left(\dfrac{n_1}{n_2}\right)\left(\dfrac{n_1}{n_2}x\right)^{\frac{n_1}{2}-1}\left(1+\dfrac{n_1}{n_2}x\right)^{-\frac{n_1+n_2}{2}}, & x\geq0\\
0, & x<0
\end{cases}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-9c7dvx2" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">性质</span>
{: id="20260305082132-qjmiahm" updated="20260305082132"}

若 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="F\sim F(n_1,n_2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，则有 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\dfrac{1}{F}\sim F(n_2,n_1)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
{: id="20260305082132-8mc7env" updated="20260305082132"}

因此有
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-vdisosh"}

$$
\huge F_\overline{1-\alpha}(n_1,n_2)=\dfrac{1}{F_\overline\alpha(n_2,n_1)}
$$
{: id="20260305082132-9lfxyt5" updated="20260305082132"}

### 4.正态总体
{: id="20260305082132-oefetdt" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是来自正太总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="N(\mu,\sigma^2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的样本，则有
{: id="20260305082132-n8ui55h" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-fxh48ls" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\overline{X}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 与 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="S^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 独立
  {: id="20260305082132-n85se07" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-o0lcetp" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge\overline{X}\sim N\left(\mu,\dfrac{\sigma^2}{n}\right)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: id="20260305082132-rr5tv0g" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-8oyjo8y" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge(n-1)\dfrac{S^2}{\sigma^2}\sim\chi^2(n-1)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-dxu6soo"}
- {: id="20260305082132-pqgxyw0" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu}{S/\sqrt{n}}\sim t(n-1)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: id="20260305082132-sfqc0p0" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-fb6xzla" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge\dfrac{S_1^2/\sigma_1^2}{S^2_2/\sigma_2^2}\sim F(n_1-1,n_2-1)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: id="20260305082132-2d7lgub" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-bux3oxr" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge\left.\dfrac{1}{n_1}\sum_{i=1}^{n_1}\left(\dfrac{X_i-\mu_1}{\sigma_1}\right)^2\middle/\dfrac{1}{n_2}\sum_{i=1}^{n_2}\left(\dfrac{Y_i-\mu_2}{\sigma_2}\right)^2\right.\sim F(n_1,n_2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: id="20260305082132-2hautpw" updated="20260305082132"}
- {: id="20260305082132-sye5fm8" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\huge \dfrac{(\overline{X}-\overline{Y})-(\mu_1-\mu_2)}{S_w}\sqrt{\dfrac{n_1n_2}{n_1+n_2}}\sim t(n_1+n_2-2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
  {: id="20260305082132-ftw52ce" updated="20260305082132"}
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-aj2hh9c"}

> $$
> \huge S^2_w=\dfrac{(n_1-1)S_1^2+(n_2-1)S_2^2}{n_1+n_2-2}
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-h875fc0" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-pa2qg1j" updated="20260305082132"}

### 5.顺序统计量
{: id="20260305082132-gujzjyb" updated="20260305082132"}

总体分布函数为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="F(x)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，概率密度为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="f(x)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，则顺序统计量 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X_i^*" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的概率密度为
{: id="20260305082132-m2i5g82" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge f_{X_i^*}(x)=\dfrac{n!}{(i-1)!(n-i)!}F^{i-1}(x)(1-F^{n-i}(x))f(x)\quad i=1,2,\cdots,n
$$
{: id="20260305082132-zmwa1lk" updated="20260305082132"}

### 6.给定统计量分布的判断方法
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-2i48bbz"}

根据正态分布的可加性，归并表达式中的随机变量，往三大分布的定义式靠
{: id="20260305082132-qvimzno" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">例</span> <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_9)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是取自正态总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的样本，令 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="Y_1=\dfrac{1}{6}\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{6}X_i" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="Y_2=\dfrac{1}{3}\displaystyle\sum_{i=7}^{9}X_i" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="S^2=\dfrac{1}{2}\displaystyle\sum_{i=7}^{9}(X_i-Y_2)^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="Z=\dfrac{\sqrt{2}(Y_1-Y_2)}{S}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，求 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="Z" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的分布。
<span data-type="strong">解</span> 设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X\sim N(\mu,\sigma^2)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>，那么有
{: id="20260305082132-qoi7dlc" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge Y_1\sim N(\mu,\dfrac{\sigma^2}{6}),Y_2\sim N(\mu,\dfrac{\sigma^2}{3})
$$
{: id="20260305082132-2mqbhh1" updated="20260305082132"}

则
{: id="20260305082132-zpo0u7s" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\sqrt{2}}{\sigma}(Y_1-Y_2)\sim N(0,1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-3o2qfla" updated="20260305082132"}

又有
{: id="20260305082132-snejw5a" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{2S^2}{\sigma^2}\sim \chi^2(2)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ls2ir9t" updated="20260305082132"}

故
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-gnylqo3"}

$$
\huge Z=\dfrac{\frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sigma}(Y_1-Y_2)}{\sqrt{\frac{2S^2}{\sigma^2}/2}}\sim t(2)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-oormpcm" updated="20260305082132"}

# 三、参数估计
{: id="20260305082132-tx4cye8" updated="20260305082132"}

## （一）点估计
{: id="20260305082132-7pc54uw" updated="20260305082132"}

### 1.矩估计
{: id="20260305082132-dmp18tz" updated="20260305082132"}

> <span data-type="strong">辛钦大数定律</span> 样本 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 阶原点矩依概率收敛于总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 阶远点矩
> {: id="20260305082132-i445o1k" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-p0bv0sp" updated="20260305082132"}

假设总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 有 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 个待估计参数，列出 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="k" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 个矩方程
{: id="20260305082132-9sbe1a3" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \alpha_j=E(X^j)=A_j=\dfrac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_i^j\quad (j=i,2,\cdots,k)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-9lc81xp"}

求解得
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-sw0f0tt"}

$$
\huge \hat{\theta}_j=\hat{\theta}_j(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)\quad(j=1,2,\cdots,k)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ozm6sxd" updated="20260305082132"}

即为矩估计量
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-xrxj47f"}

### 2.极大似然估计
{: id="20260305082132-mibcr45" updated="20260305082132"}

对总体 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="X" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的样本做一次观测得到观测值，计算该事件发生的概率，即为似然函数
{: id="20260305082132-a8a3mey" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge L(\theta)=\prod_{i=1}^nf(x_i;\theta)=\prod_{i=1}^nP(X_i=x_i;\theta)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-5avvz68" updated="20260305082132"}

若存在 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat{\theta}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 使得
{: id="20260305082132-yuoz64f" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge L(\hat{\theta})=\max_{\theta\in\Theta}L(\theta)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-d5ig4rq" updated="20260305082132"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat{\theta}(x_1,x_2,\cdots,x_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的极大似然估计值
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-wx6puh2"}

若 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="f(x)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 可微，则可求解如下方程组
{: id="20260305082132-x6rainn" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\partial L(\theta)}{\partial\theta_i}=0\quad or \quad \dfrac{\partial\ln{L(\theta)}}{\partial\theta_i}\quad(i=1,2,\cdots,k)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-qwh8prm" updated="20260305082132"}

若方程无解，则需根据 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 取值空间 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\Theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 与定义求解
{: id="20260305082132-m7cghg8" updated="20260305082132"}

## （二）估计量的评选标准
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-ried2kw"}

### 1.无偏性
{: id="20260305082132-64i2yau" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="strong">定义</span> 设 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat{\theta}(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 是 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的估计量，若对任意 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta\in\Theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 有
{: id="20260305082132-xlpz9eb" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge E(\hat\theta)=\theta
$$
{: id="20260305082132-ol2cexk" updated="20260305082132"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的<span data-type="strong">无偏估计量</span>
{: id="20260305082132-kohim1n" updated="20260305082132"}

记
{: id="20260305082132-phj39cx" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge b_n=E(\hat\theta)-\theta
$$
{: id="20260305082132-s7kr7ii" updated="20260305082132"}

为估计量的偏差，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="b_n\neq0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 则为<span data-type="strong">有偏估计</span>。若
{: id="20260305082132-du1esmb" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}b_n=0
$$
{: id="20260305082132-qyge8sh" updated="20260305082132"}

则称为<span data-type="strong">渐进无偏估计</span>
{: id="20260305082132-5fum8e3" updated="20260305082132"}

> 无偏估计量的函数不一定是无偏估计
> {: id="20260305082132-mbaqwjp" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-napo9xq" updated="20260305082132"}

### 2.有效性
{: id="20260305082132-k2d557p" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta_1,\hat\theta_2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 都是 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的无偏估计量，若
{: id="20260305082132-lprwh9p" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge D(\hat\theta_1)<D(\hat\theta_2)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-y9fhyph" updated="20260305082132"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta_1" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 较 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta_2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 有效
{: id="20260305082132-nawwrv8" updated="20260305082132"}

若对任一无偏估计量 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 都有
{: id="20260305082132-hphcau4" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge D(\hat\theta_0)\leq D(\hat\theta)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-o1uqoc8" updated="20260305082132"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta_0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为<span data-type="strong">最小方差无偏估计量</span>（<span data-type="strong">最优无偏估计量</span>）
{: id="20260305082132-w38a170" updated="20260305082132"}

### 3.一致性
{: id="20260305082132-ic6s814" updated="20260305082132"}

若对任意 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta\in\Theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 与任意 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\varepsilon&amp;gt;0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 有
{: id="20260305082132-h0m70j0" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}P(|\hat\theta(X_1,X_2,\cdots,X_n)-\theta|\leq\varepsilon)=1
$$
{: id="20260305082132-28vxhvt" updated="20260305082132"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\hat\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为<span data-type="strong">一致估计量</span>
{: id="20260305082132-fr355ih" updated="20260305082132"}

## （三）区间估计
{: id="20260305082132-93kye0j" updated="20260305082132"}

若存在 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\underline{\theta}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 和 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\overline{\theta}" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 满足
{: id="20260305082132-xekiuu6" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge P(\underline\theta<\theta<\overline\theta)=1-\alpha
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-jxddee5"}

则称 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="(\underline\theta,\overline\theta)" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 为参数 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的置信水平为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="1-\alpha" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的置信区间，<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\underline\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 和 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\overline\theta" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 称为置信下限和置信上限
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-c32unpe"}

<span data-type="strong">方法</span> 选取分布已知的枢轴量（带有一个待估参数的随机变量的函数），找到枢轴量发生概率为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="1-\alpha" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 的区间，反解出待估参数的区间，即为置信区间
{: id="20260305082132-0y8u3m9" updated="20260305082132"}

### 1.单个正态总体均值的区间估计
{: id="20260305082132-ao51kcr" updated="20260305082132"}

#### （1）<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 已知
{: id="20260305082132-geqnd6j" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}\sim N(0,1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-eoj4kxj" updated="20260305082132"}

有
{: id="20260305082132-0ne45f5" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge P\left(-u_{\alpha/2}<\dfrac{\overline X-\mu}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}<u_{\alpha/2}\right)=1-\alpha
$$
{: id="20260305082132-k174dlb" updated="20260305082132"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-mfdvn4c" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\overline X-\dfrac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n}}u_{\alpha/2},\overline X+\dfrac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n}}u_{\alpha/2}\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-sefb6ij" updated="20260305082132"}

> 对应的单侧置信区间，将 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\alpha/2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 改为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\alpha" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 即可
> {: id="20260305082132-4zgko8j" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-q1le0fe" updated="20260305082132"}

#### （2）<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 未知
{: id="20260305082132-jma5a4k" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\overline X-\mu}{S/\sqrt{n}}\sim t(n-1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-g9f44km" updated="20260305082132"}

有
{: id="20260305082132-lmjkn4e" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge P\left(-t_{\alpha/2}(n-1)<\dfrac{\overline X-\mu}{S/\sqrt{n}}<t_{\alpha/2}(n-1)\right)=1-\alpha
$$
{: id="20260305082132-e2uewkb" updated="20260305082132"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-8b27m8l" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\overline X-\dfrac{S}{\sqrt{n}}t_{\alpha/2}(n-1),\overline X+\dfrac{S}{\sqrt{n}}t_{\alpha/2}(n-1)\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-istztfq" updated="20260305082132"}

> 对应的单侧置信区间，将 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\alpha/2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 改为 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\alpha" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 即可
> {: id="20260305082132-wort196" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-jvuo3fn" updated="20260305082132"}

### 2.单个正态总体方差的估计
{: id="20260305082132-gujnrbq" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\mu" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 未知
{: id="20260305082132-443uwsk" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{(n-1)S^2}{\sigma^2}\sim\chi^2(n-1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-hk0veff" updated="20260305082132"}

有
{: id="20260305082132-f2crzvm" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge P\left(\chi^2_{1-\alpha/2}(n-1)<\dfrac{(n-1)S^2}{\sigma^2}<\chi^2_{\alpha/2}(n-1)\right)=1-\alpha
$$
{: id="20260305082132-t63qi3a" updated="20260305082132"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-7de76i8" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\dfrac{(n-1)S^2}{\chi^2_{\alpha/2}(n-1)},\dfrac{(n-1)S^2}{\chi^2_{1-\alpha/2}(n-1)}\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-klsnob4" updated="20260305082132"}

### 3.两个正态总体均值差的估计
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-16v5odc"}

#### （1）<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2_1" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 与 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2_2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 均已知
{: id="20260305082132-7pn3sty" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\overline X-\overline Y-(\mu_1-\mu_2)}{\sqrt{\dfrac{\sigma^2_1}{n_1}+\dfrac{\sigma^2_2}{n_2}}}\sim N(0,1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-2r5ghw4" updated="20260305082132"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-lt68xcr" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\overline X-\overline Y-\sqrt{\dfrac{\sigma^2_1}{n_1}+\dfrac{\sigma^2_2}{n_2}}u_{\alpha/2},\overline X-\overline Y+\sqrt{\dfrac{\sigma^2_1}{n_1}+\dfrac{\sigma^2_2}{n_2}}u_{\alpha/2}\right)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-o44muk2"}

#### （2）方差未知，但 <span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma_1^2=\sigma^2_2=\sigma^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>
{: id="20260305082132-zcyz8y4" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{\overline X-\overline Y-(\mu_1-\mu_2)}{S_w\sqrt{\dfrac{1}{n_1}+\dfrac{1}{n_2}}}\sim t(n_1+n_2-2)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-d9fyygv"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-o529i59" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\overline X-\overline Y-t_{\alpha/2}(n_1+n_2-2)S_w\sqrt{\dfrac{1}{n_1}+\dfrac{1}{n_2}},\overline X-\overline Y+t_{\alpha/2}(n_1+n_2-2)S_w\sqrt{\dfrac{1}{n_1}+\dfrac{1}{n_2}}\right)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-dmxy6jb"}

### 4.两个正态总体方差比的区间估计
{: id="20260305082132-2r0xdop" updated="20260305082132"}

<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\mu_1,\mu_2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 未知
{: id="20260305082132-1j9yh44" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \dfrac{S_1^2/\sigma_1^2}{S_2^2/\sigma_2^2}\sim F(n_1-1,n_2-1)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-3fyostq" updated="20260305082132"}

置信区间为
{: id="20260305082132-p8l0fmi" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge \left(\dfrac{S^2_1}{S^2_2}\dfrac{1}{F_{\alpha/2}(n_1-1,n_2-1)},\dfrac{S^2_1}{S^2_2}\dfrac{1}{F_{1-\alpha/2}(n_1-1,n_2-1)}\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-pqp520c" updated="20260305082132"}

# 四、假设检验
{: id="20260305082132-1kl1r0e" updated="20260305082132"}

||<span data-type="strong inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="H_0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span><span data-type="strong"> 为真</span>|<span data-type="strong inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="H_0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span><span data-type="strong"> 为假</span>|
| :-: | :--------: | :--------: |
|<span data-type="strong">接受 </span><span data-type="strong inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="H_0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>|正确|第二类错误|
|<span data-type="strong">拒绝 </span><span data-type="strong inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="H_0" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span>|第一类错误|正确|
{: id="20260305082132-jgd835u" updated="20260305082132"}

## （一）参数假设检验
{: id="20260305082132-e2mw7iw" updated="20260305082132"}

### 1.单个正态总体均值的假设检验
{: id="20260305082132-e4u7bft" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-x1qeg2i" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">双侧假设检验</span>
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-9ggk9op"}
{: id="20260305082132-ifskbou" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge H_0:\mu=\mu_0,\quad H_1:\mu\neq\mu_0
$$
{: id="20260305082132-cv0fe26" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-jy4cqr4" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">右边单侧检验</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-hdui3lw" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-6hgiri3" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge H_0:\mu\leq\mu_0:\quad H_1:\mu>\mu_0
$$
{: id="20260305082132-i662d6b" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-a7w3j9o" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">左边单侧检验</span>
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-lueus59"}
{: id="20260305082132-laf3up6" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge H_0:\mu\geq\mu_0,\quad H_1:\mu<\mu_0
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-b99llqc"}

#### （1）<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 已知
{: id="20260305082132-e1rc7ib" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-5tb2i41"}<span data-type="strong">双侧</span>
  {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-6lco6mh"}
{: id="20260305082132-7vr7wol" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\left|\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}\right|>u_{\frac{\alpha}{2}}\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-cu2mkvn" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-v7sh3bc" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">右侧</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-axgwpa2" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-dy3r1ap" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}>u_\alpha\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-vrdcxpc" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-1j8rowu" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">左侧</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-wvg9ewp" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-0x0n39p" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}<-u_\alpha\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-60njzzk" updated="20260305082132"}

#### （2）<span data-type="inline-math" data-subtype="math" data-content="\sigma^2" contenteditable="false" class="render-node"></span> 未知
{: id="20260305082132-adwtblq" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-0lunro5" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">双侧</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-vf4a7ny" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-0alr436" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\left|\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{S/\sqrt{n}}\right|>t_{\alpha/2}(n-1)\right)
$$
{: id="20260305082132-lie24s0" updated="20260305082132"}

- {: id="20260305082132-hr21d0z" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">右侧</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-0idz2z2" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-kqewtfp" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{S/\sqrt{n}}>t_{\alpha}(n-1)\right)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-urfvg5y"}

- {: id="20260305082132-iwos0jd" updated="20260305082132"}<span data-type="strong">左侧</span>
  {: id="20260305082132-mgp5ci9" updated="20260305082132"}
{: id="20260305082132-6qsgd16" updated="20260305082132"}

$$
\huge W=\left(\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{S/\sqrt{n}}<-t_{\alpha}(n-1)\right)
$$
{: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-882ntt1"}

> 总体分布未知但为大样本时有
> {: updated="20260305082132" id="20260305082132-jlt5sel"}
>
> $$
> \huge U=\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}或\dfrac{\overline{X}-\mu_0}{S/\sqrt{n}}\sim N(0,1)
> $$
> {: id="20260305082132-gt5balr" updated="20260305082132"}
>
{: id="20260305082132-l13a2c2" updated="20260305082132"}

